PickupObject_1:
(:action PickupObject_1
        :parameters (?toolObject - object ?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object)

        :precondition (and 
		(objectType ?toolObject MugType)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
		(not (holdsAny ?a))
		(holds ?a ?toolObject)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(holds ?a ?o)
		)
)
